'''拉謙·沙基·史達寧'''{{MBE}}（{{lang-en|Raheem Shaquille Sterling}}，{{bd|1994年|12月8日|catidx=Raheem, Sterling}}），是一名[[牙買加|牙買加]]裔[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員。曾效力[[英超|英超]]俱樂部[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]，目前效力於[[英超|英超]]俱樂部[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]，亦为[[英格兰国家队|英格兰国家队]]成员。

== 球會 ==
=== 昆士柏流浪 ===
在加盟利物浦之前，史達寧曾在昆士柏流浪青年隊當上學徒7年。

=== 利物浦 ===
史達寧在2010年2月以60萬英鎊轉會費加盟[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]。

在2011年2月14日，史達寧在一場英格蘭足總青年盃對修安聯的比賽中，個人取得5個入球，最終球隊以9-0大勝修安聯。

2012年8月26日，史達寧在英超首次以正選身份出場迎戰[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]，該場比賽中史達寧表現搶鏡，史達寧賽後被[[天空體育台|天空體育台]]評為全場最佳球員。

=== 曼城 ===
[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]同意以4900萬英鎊（含500萬附加）將史達寧售至[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]。

史達寧於[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]表現出色。

斯特林在瓜迪奥拉的带领下定期为曼城出场，参加了2016-2017赛季的开幕赛。他在三场比赛中打进两球并提供一次助攻，成为2016年8月的英超联赛最佳球员。

== 國家隊 ==
史達寧曾為英格蘭U16和U17青年軍代表。<ref>{{cite web |title=Raheem Sterling |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/All-Teams/Players/S/Raheem-Sterling |work=TheFA.com |publisher=The Football Association |accessdate=22 April 2011 |archive-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IHbivOsJ?url=http://www.thefa.com/England/All-Teams/Players/S/Raheem-Sterling |dead-url=no }}</ref> 同時他也有資格選擇為他的出生地，牙買加出戰。而他的母親納迪娜已表示她希望看到史達寧會在國際賽中為[[牙買加國家足球隊|牙買加]]披甲上陣。<ref>{{cite web |title='I'd Love To See Him Play For Jamaica' |url=http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20100302/sports/sports2.html |work=Jamaica Gleaner |publisher=Gleaner Company |date=2 March 2010 |accessdate=22 April 2011 |archive-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IHbkzgwG?url=http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20100302/sports/sports2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

史達寧在[[2011年U17世界盃足球賽|2011年U17世界盃足球賽]]入選到[[英格蘭17歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭]]大軍名單當中。他在[[帕丘卡|帕丘卡]]對{{le|盧旺達17歲以下足球代表隊|Rwanda national under-17 football team|盧旺達}}的首戰中射入了一球長距離遠射，助英格蘭以2-0取得了開門紅。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13839092.stm|title=Rwanda beaten by England in World U17 opener|date=20 June 2011|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=21 June 2011|archive-date=2013-07-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IHbmDrNA?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13839092|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他亦在對{{le|阿根廷17歲以下足球代表隊|Argentina national under-17 football team|阿根廷}}的16強戰中射入扳平一球，令英格蘭在後來的十二碼大戰中得以4-2勝出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/3270/england-national-team/2011/07/01/2555329/england-under-17s-to-face-germany-in-the-quarter-finals-of|title=England Under-17s to face Germany in the quarter-finals of the World Cup following victory over Argentina on penalties|date=1 July 2011|work=goal.com|accessdate=14 July 2011|archive-date=2013-07-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IHboCEbX?url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/3270/england-national-team/2011/07/01/2555329/england-under-17s-to-face-germany-in-the-quarter-finals-of|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，史達寧被[[英格蘭國家足球隊|英格蘭]]徵召參與[[2018年世界盃足球賽|2018年世界盃足球賽]]的賽事<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44138600 |title=England World Cup squad: Trent Alexander-Arnold in 23-man squad |website=BBC Sport |date=16 May 2018 |access-date=17 May 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713131712/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44138600 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該屆英格蘭以殿軍結束世界盃之旅。

2021年5月，史達寧再次被英格蘭徵召參與[[2020年歐洲國家盃|2020年歐洲國家盃]]的賽事<ref>{{cite web|url=https://footballexpress.co.uk/ben-white-replaces-taa-in-england-squad-ahead-of-euro-2020/|title=Ben White Replaces TAA in England squad ahead of Euro 2020|website=Football Express.co.uk|date=8 June 2021|access-date=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624202800/https://footballexpress.co.uk/ben-white-replaces-taa-in-england-squad-ahead-of-euro-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並於小組賽第一場與第三場分別面對[[克羅埃西亞國家足球隊|克羅埃西亞]]以及[[捷克國家足球隊|捷克]]的兩場比賽中均攻入全場唯一一顆進球帶領球隊獲勝前進淘汰賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51197735 |title=England's Euro 2020 campaign got off to a winning start as Raheem Sterling's goal secured victory over Croatia at Wembley |date=13 June 2021 |via=www.bbc.co.uk |access-date=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624235743/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51197735 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/51198446 |title=Czech Republic 0–1 England |date=22 June 2021 |via=www.bbc.co.uk |access-date=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2021-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628220112/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/51198446 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。更在十六強淘汰賽階段面對[[德國國家足球隊|德國]]時於第75分鐘率先攻破德國大門，帶領球隊以2:0收下勝利並前進八強賽<ref>{{Cite news|title=England end 55-year wait for knockout win over Germany|language=en-GB|work=BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51198606|access-date=2021-06-29|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701085405/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51198606|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。
雖然英格蘭於[[2020年歐洲足球錦標賽決賽|2020年歐洲國家盃決賽]]的[[點球大戰|點球大戰]]中以2:3敗給[[義大利國家足球隊|義大利]]，最終以亞軍坐收<ref name="#1">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51198762 |title=England lose shootout in Euro 2020 final |first=Phil |last=McNulty |work=BBC Sport |date=11 July 2021 |access-date=11 July 2021 |archive-date=2021-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711170405/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51198762 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是史達林的表現仍舊出色，榮獲該屆歐國盃官方最佳陣容<ref>{{cite news|title=official UEFA EURO 2020 Team of the Tournament|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/026b-12be97f0eb56-3ce3b8794fa7-1000--euro-2020-team-of-the-tournament/|publisher=uefa.com|date=13 July 2021|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713094259/https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro-2020/news/026b-12be97f0eb56-3ce3b8794fa7-1000--euro-2020-team-of-the-tournament/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
史達寧從小長大於[[金斯敦|金斯敦]]的萬魏利區，並由其祖母一手撫養。<ref>{{cite news |first=André |last=Lowe |title=As Hype Grows Around Raheem Sterling |url=http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20110223/sports/sports3.html |work=Jamaica Gleaner |publisher=Gleaner Company |date=23 February 2011 |accessdate=22 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110817022936/http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20110223/sports/sports3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他的高中生涯就讀於[[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]]的雨山高校。<ref>{{cite news |title=History boys: Dalglish to get teenage kicks in Prague with Liverpool starlet Sterling |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1357492/Liverpool-set-make-Raheem-Sterling-youngest-player-Europa-League-tie.html |work=Mail Online |publisher=Associated Newspapers |date=16 February 2011 |accessdate=22 April 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083304/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1357492/Liverpool-set-make-Raheem-Sterling-youngest-player-Europa-League-tie.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

斯特林是[[基督教|基督徒]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2264635/Raheem-Sterling--The-Footballers-Football-Column-Branislav-Ivanovic-scariest-man-Ive-played-hes-dirty-hes-tank.html |title=RAHEEM STERLING: I get kicked a lot - it's annoying trying to sleep with your legs in pieces... Ivanovic is the scariest man I've played against but he's not dirty, he's a tank |access-date=2014-07-27 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022025009/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2264635/Raheem-Sterling--The-Footballers-Football-Column-Branislav-Ivanovic-scariest-man-Ive-played-hes-dirty-hes-tank.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

